{"tid":550737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國男子打獵時被從天而降的死鵝擊中頭部受傷","createTime":"2018-02-05T04:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T06:01:39.000Z","uid":53379,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a59a79c0a7a47761dec363f8ee92cb724757ff8b","tid":550737,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國男子打獵時被從天而降的死鵝擊中頭部受傷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2018/2/mse4fidze54l6xu6pfg4zpcy9b3s29.jpg?auto=compress&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=648&amp;q=100&amp;updated_at=2018-02-04-10-30-47&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2018%2F2%2Fmse4fidze54l6xu6pfg4zpcy9b3s29.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26fit%3Dcrop%26h%3D648%26q%3D100%26updated_at%3D2018-02-04-10-30-47%26w%3D1080&h=d27188e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名獵人被一隻從天而降的加拿大鵝擊中暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n51歲的Robert Meilhammer與另外三名男子在馬里蘭州東岸打獵，去到米爾斯河（Miles River）附近時，一群加拿大鵝飛過，一名男子舉槍射中其中一隻，被擊斃的鵝墜落，擊中Robert Meilhammer，他臉部和頭都受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當地救援人員形容Robert Meilhammer傷勢嚴重，並掉了兩顆牙齒。目前情況已轉趨穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬里蘭州自然資源警察Candy Thomson表示，加拿大鵝重10至14磅，當牠們伸展翅膀時，可以長達6尺：「如果牠們在60尺上空墜下，剛好落在你的頭部，那必然會造成嚴重傷害。」<br />\n<br />\n現在是加拿大鵝北遷的季節，獵人紛紛湧到東岸狩獵。當地警察表示，雖然事件有點不可思議，但並非聞所未聞。又指當獵人專注狩獵目標，對周邊事物警覺性或會降低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/89098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F89098&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBunadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=79ab73ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/89098</a>"},{"pid":"1d0e369d50750a8d35dee292d322f4154b5e4814","tid":550737,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be45bf61ffe5244bc03e720808ffb6947b95b2f9","tid":5507